node.text:
Tonight I will be helping Raise Money for @gktwvillage .. I’ll be reading to the Children at 7pm eat .. if your interested in donating Text44321  and if your interested in watching the live stream go to my story and swipe up ❤️❤️❤️ #givingtuesdaynow 
Each month more than 700 children are waiting for their wishes due COVID-19, but on this #GivingTuesdayNow  we're showing them the hope and magic that's in store for them at the Village. Join us to help #givehopetowishes

node.text: Hey guys it’s me Baby Cameron again! My monthly takeover of mommies Instagram! I’m 4 months old today.. I love when my mommy tells me stories and sings to me ..she really makes me laugh! I love playing with my big brother CJ.. he’s teaching me so many things.. I can’t wait until I can run around and play with him! Daddy makes fart noises and tickles me and I belly laugh every time ! I love my family ! My mommy is starting to show me how to pet Cali she’s very soft! I love her ❤️ I’m still not loving tummy time but I’m becoming stronger and stronger .. smiling is my favorite and I just love all the kisses and cuddles .. I’m a real mushy baby 🥰🤗 okay I’m gonna go cuddle with mommy and brother on this rainy day! Thanks for following my journey ❤️❤️ ps. How much do me and my big brother CJ look alike ! He’s my best friend ☺️
